comments: Embiid (PHI) is firming up over his right foot when marginal side-to-side contact occurs with McBride (NYK) as McBride moves over the pick.
Robinson (NYK) initiates arm contact with Embiid (PHI) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) and Robinson (NYK) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Brunson (NYK) jumps to Lowry's (PHI) side to contest the jump shot attempt, and the marginal body contact after the release is the result of Lowry slightly extending outward toward Brunson.
Lowry (PHI) legally contests Hart's (NYK) jump shot.  There is no camera angle that shows illegal contact.
Robinson (NYK) lowers his arm and initiates contact with Maxey's (PHI) face and left arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) brings his left hand toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with Brunson's (NYK) front as Brunson dribbles across half-court.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) initiates contact across Brunson's (NYK) right arm and affects Brunson's SQBR after he picks up his dribble.
Brunson (NYK) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Embiid (PHI) commits a take foul on Robinson (NYK). The contact with Brunson (NYK) occurs after the whistle.
Embiid (PHI) is firming up over his left foot and absorbs the contact from McBride (NYK) to his upper body.
Robinson (NYK) turns slightly towards Maxey (PHI), and the contact as they come together during the drive is marginal.
Robinson (NYK) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Lowry (PHI) brings his left hand toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with McBride's (NYK) left side/leg after he receives the pass.
Embiid (PHI) applies his hand to Anunoby's (NYK) side, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Brunson (NYK) slides his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) brings his forearm towards Brunson's (NYK) upper body, and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Brunson (NYK) gathers the ball in the air and takes his first step on his left foot before legally releasing the ball to pass.
Lowry (PHI) is moving forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Anunoby (NYK) as Anunoby steps back toward the free throw line.
Lowry (PHI) legally contests Anunoby's (NYK) jump shot.  There is no camera angle that shows illegal contact.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) commits a take foul on Hart (NYK).
